Package: coursepackR
Type: Package
Title: Course Tools for From Vibes to Variables
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Alex P.", "Leith", email = "aleith@siue.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Alex P. Leith [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Alex P. Leith <aleith@siue.edu>
Description: Student-facing R package for MC-451 Research Methods at SIUE.
    Provides helper functions to download weekly course materials, manage
    research projects, access the bundled music dataset, and integrate
    RStudio with Obsidian-based workflows. Includes the unified music
    dataset and textbook chapters from "From Vibes to Variables: A Field
    Guide to Open Media Science."
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
